Package: AgCargoPestRisk
Title: Agricultural Cargo Pest Risk Assessment Pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dalon", "White", , "dalon.white@usda.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for assessing pest risks associated with 
    agricultural cargo imports. Provides functions for retrieving diagnostic data,
    integrating pest impact assessments (OPEP, FNW, HLI), and calculating risk
    scores for commodity-origin combinations at ports of entry.
